{
  "title": "Master Survey Build",
  "showProgressBar": "bottom",
  "pages": [
    {
      "name": "lndgRoot_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lndgRootPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>About this survey</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgRootText",
              "html": "<p>This survey asks detailed questions about your experience with laryngeal paralysis and how it affected your companion animal's life. </p> <p>We know how hard it is to lose one's beloved companion. If you're still grieving from the loss, maybe it's best to do the survey later when you've had time to heal. </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgCrossedOverHeading",
              "html": "<h3>About your LP companion<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgCrossedOverText",
              "html": "<p>If you think you'd like to continue, please tell us your companion's name and if your companion has crossed over the Rainbow Bridge. This will allow us to personalize the survey to your individual situation.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lndgCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "lndgCmpnName",
                  "title": "Please tell us your companion's name:",
                  "isRequired": true
                },
                {
                  "type": "imagepicker",
                  "name": "lndgCrossedOver",
                  "title": "Has your companion crossed over the Rainbow Bridge?",
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "choices": [
                    {
                      "value": "deceased",
                      "imageLink": "./img-companions-rainbow.png",
                      "text": "Crossed over"
                    },
                    {
                      "value": "living",
                      "imageLink": "./img-companions.png",
                      "text": "Still with us"
                    }
                  ],
                  "imageWidth": 120,
                  "imageHeight": 120,
                  "showLabel": true
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lndgMakeSelection",
              "html": "<p>Once you've made your selection, please choose 'Next' to begin the survey.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lvngRoot_page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngRootPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "lndgCompanionName",
              "placeholder": "fake"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootHeading",
              "html": "<h2>Laryngeal Paralysis Survey Questions</h2>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootText",
              "html": "<p>We know how hard it is to deal with LarPar. There are no simple questions, no clear-cut answers, and all the choices are lesser-evil ones. </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngRootWhyContact",
              "html": "<img src='/img-info-icon.png' class='survey-info-icon' alt='Example image' />&nbsp;<a href='https://example.com' class='survey-info-link' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'>Why provide a contact?</a>"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "lvngRootUserContact",
              "title": "Facebook account name or email",
              "isRequired": true
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngCmpnAboutCompHeading",
              "html": "<h3>Tell us about {lndgCompanionName}!<h3>"
            },
            {
              "type": "html",
              "name": "lvngCmpnAboutCompText",
              "html": "<p>We're focusing on dogs right now, but if you have a horse or cat with LP, feel free to answer the questions as best as you can. If a question doesn't apply, just leave it blank and skip to the next one.  </p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "panel",
              "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsPanel",
              "elements": [
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel1",
                  "title": "What is your companion's name and breed or breed mix?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnName",
                      "title": "Name:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnBreed",
                      "title": "Breed or mix:",
                      "isRequired": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel2",
                  "title": "What is your companion's age (in years and months) and gender?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnAgeYears",
                      "title": "Age in years (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "min": "1",
                      "max": "40",
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 40,
                          "text": "Age must be between 1 and 40"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnAgeMonths",
                      "title": "Months (number 1 - 12)",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "min": 1,
                      "max": 12,
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 12,
                          "text": "Months must be between 1 and 12"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnGender",
                      "title": "Gender:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Female",
                      "labelFalse": "Male"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel3",
                  "title": "About how much does your companion weigh in pounds or kilos?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnWeight",
                      "title": "Weight (number):",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "inputType": "number",
                      "min": 1,
                      "max": 2200,
                      "validators": [
                        {
                          "type": "numeric",
                          "minValue": 1,
                          "maxValue": 2200,
                          "text": "Weight must be between 1 and 2200"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "boolean",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnWeightUnits",
                      "title": "Please choose pounds or kilos:",
                      "isRequired": true,
                      "labelTrue": "Kg",
                      "labelFalse": "Lbs"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "panel",
                  "name": "lvngCmpnDetailsSubpanel4",
                  "title": "How energetic, excitable, or anxious is your companion (1=very calm, 5=very excitable)?",
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "type": "rating",
                      "name": "lvngCmpnExcitable",
                      "title": ""
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
